# KYLYVNYK CLUB — Cursor AI Rules (root shorthand)

# Full rules are in .cursor/rules/\*.md and AGENT.md

## Stack

Next.js 15 App Router · React 19 · TypeScript 5 strict · Tailwind v4
tRPC v11 · Prisma · Supabase Postgres · Auth.js v5 · next-intl
@kyc/ui · @kyc/api · @kyc/db · @kyc/i18n · @kyc/config (turborepo pnpm)

## Critical Rules Memorized

1. ZERO hardcoded strings — only i18n keys from @kyc/i18n
2. ZERO direct Prisma calls outside @kyc/api procedures
3. ZERO `any` type — TypeScript strict everywhere
4. ALL deletes = soft delete (deletedAt field)
5. ALL admin mutations = auditedAdminProcedure + AuditLog write
6. ALWAYS add keys to RU + EN + UK simultaneously
7. ALWAYS add loading skeletons and empty states
8. ALWAYS wrap non-critical side effects (email, push, audit) in try/catch
9. NEVER expose secrets in NEXT_PUBLIC\_ vars
10. NEVER skip rate limiting on public mutations
11. DEFAULT to Server Components — "use client" only when required
12. PREFER cursor pagination not offset
13. ALWAYS sanitize audit payloads via sanitizeForAudit()
14. NEW component → add to @kyc/ui with Storybook story first

## Packages (Never Install Alternatives)

Styling: Tailwind v4 + CVA + clsx + tailwind-merge
Icons: lucide-react (tree-shake — named imports only)
Animation: framer-motion (gate with NEXT_PUBLIC_DISABLE_ANIMATIONS)
State: Zustand (UI) + TanStack Query (server)
Forms: react-hook-form + zodResolver + Zod
Auth: Auth.js v5 (web: credentials+Google+magic-link · admin: credentials+TOTP)
Email: Resend + @react-email/components
Files: uploadthing
Push: web-push + Serwist SW
Realtime: Supabase Realtime (chat only)
Maps: react-leaflet (dynamic import, ssr:false)
Charts: recharts (admin dashboard only)

## FSD Layers (No Upward Imports)

app → widgets → features → entities → shared → @kyc/\*

## Response Format When Writing Code

1. State which files you are creating/modifying
2. Show full file contents (not snippets) for new files
3. Show targeted diffs for modifications to existing files
4. List Acceptance Criteria at the end
5. List any manual steps (env vars, migrations, seed) clearly